    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于”狙击枪”套装</h2><br>你所喜欢的武器现在都有好看的迷彩，喜欢战斗风格武器的玩家一定会喜欢。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/23afab92162f0a44ee73b500eb177a90.poster.avif?t=1685625847\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/23afab92162f0a44ee73b500eb177a90.webm?t=1685625847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/23afab92162f0a44ee73b500eb177a90.mp4?t=1685625847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用这把武器来获取无限力量！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/00287ea13d6f583c87f292e7f4dfca2e.poster.avif?t=1685625847\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/00287ea13d6f583c87f292e7f4dfca2e.webm?t=1685625847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/00287ea13d6f583c87f292e7f4dfca2e.mp4?t=1685625847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>系列中有8种武器，都合适多样的战斗情况！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >АК &quot;Alpha&quot; &quot;福波斯&quot;</h2>AK 阿尔法是一种革命性的武器升级方法。一支由以色列国防军特种部队中精心挑选出来的专业神枪手和工程师组成的团队设计了这款阿尔法步枪。这样，射手就能够使用世界上最可靠的武器最大限度地发挥他的射击能力了。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/44a953daf91f480ce68ba19e6ff58149.avif?t=1685625847\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Typhoon F12 &quot;福波斯&quot;</h2>台风 F12 特别版消音器、台风 F12 特别版抑制器、台风 F12 战术握把、台风 F12 特别版握把、瞄具台风 F12 是一把顶尖的弹匣供弹战术霰弹枪！武器精度比较高，这样你可以一射击击杀面对你的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/fc22bc4bd2ec1ffb98f611d235d35abc.avif?t=1685625847\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kriss Super V Custom &quot;福波斯&quot;</h2>Kriss Super V 得名于一种印尼剑或大刀。Kriss Super V Classic即使是在连续射击中也能保持极高的精准度，是适合各种情况的可靠之选。此外，它还自带消音器。此外，武器外观很独特<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/da2a5eccd4ad8ce3c009f9f4427b606b.avif?t=1685625847\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CDX-MC Kraken &quot;福波斯&quot;</h2>北海巨妖是一款多口径步枪，采用创新的枪管更换系统。与市场上的其他型号相比，这种多口径系统在相同枪管的拆卸和重装时，具有最低的冲击点转换。单个螺钉固定可拆卸底座，可实现短枪机口径和长枪机口径之间的快速切换。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/00bf60466af003595b21e28b51ac4e8c.avif?t=1685625847\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >M60E4 &quot;福波斯&quot;</h2>M60E4 是对萨科防务公司的 M60E3 的进一步改良。该枪可换用三种不同样式的枪管，使用改进后的弹链，更大的拉力使装弹量得以提升。容量是200多子弹，允许玩家在PvP和PvE种消灭敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/5913da3039c288186f6ff657a3a8407c.avif?t=1685625847\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SAP6 &quot;福波斯&quot;</h2>短管 SAP6 弹匣供弹式重装霰弹枪。它的新设计特色包含一个重装单体式四轨系统和一个经过重新设计的铝质泵握把，配合内置垂直前握把使用。武器主要竞争对手是MAG-7和Fabarm STF 12 Compact。可拆卸式弹匣的使用确保能在不牺牲弹匣容量的前提下，让枪管更短。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/9111329dce42e679359188d8ef700bcf.avif?t=1685625847\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PP-2000 &quot;福波斯&quot;</h2>PP2000 是一款俄罗斯冲锋枪，由图拉仪器制造设计局制造。它的高射速和高伤害尤其适合在近距离战斗中施展。武器容量是45子弹，换弹速度一般。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/5643377320d8e3cd42f9d4f365a2d705.avif?t=1685625847\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ORSIS Т-5000 &quot;福波斯&quot;</h2>Orsis T-5000 是一款俄罗斯栓动狙击步枪。武器具有高精准度，且有很大几率一发毙命，现在，即使是防护手套和防护靴也无法在近距离和中距离战斗中拯救你的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/696e635b1148e8634d488aa1ad23c6dc.avif?t=1685625847\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>理所当然玩家可以通过使用这些武器来得到更多成就。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753620/extras/68b4294deb6449b0eb7bab7b1b308a71.avif?t=1685625847\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>支付好之后请稍等15分钟左右。如果物品还没到账的话，请重新启动游戏。",
